data.description: Fantastic 2 bed, 2.5 bath townhome with awesome lake views. Property features a spacious open courtyard patio that is fully fenced in. Main level has half bath with inside laundry room, great room, dining area and has storage under the stairs. 2nd floor has master bedroom and guest room with terrific lake views. Beautiful ceramic tile throughout. Kitchen has updated appliances. Community offer pool, sidewalks and hand ball courts. Great location, close to schools, shopping and I95.
